@startuml
title Sequence: Leave request and approval
actor Student
participant "Browser / UI" as UI
participant "Leave View" as LeaveView
participant "HOD / Admin" as HOD
database "Leave DB" as DB

Student -> UI: Submit leave form
UI -> LeaveView: POST leave request
LeaveView -> DB: Save request
DB --> LeaveView: Confirm saved
LeaveView -> HOD: Notify for approval
HOD --> LeaveView: Approve / Reject
LeaveView -> DB: Update status
DB --> LeaveView: Confirm update
LeaveView -> UI: Notify student
@enduml
